Blurb::
Specify the name of the work directory created by Dakota
Description::
The \c named keyword allows the user to specify the name of
the work directory created by Dakota. 
The directory will be created as a subdirectory of the directory in which Dakota is invoked.

The \c directory_tag keyword will append the function evaluation number to the name.

